dcterms:description: The Room Crossing One dataset consists of RGB images captured from a drone flying through a simulated environment. It includes 18 different rooms with varying obstacles, including a block, a wall, and an overhang, designed to test navigation control.
dcterms:title: Room Crossing One

dcterms:description: The Room Crossing Two dataset is a more challenging version of the Room Crossing One dataset, consisting of RGB images captured from a drone in a simulated environment. It is designed to represent a real-world imitation learning scenario with fewer training examples.
dcterms:title: Room Crossing Two
